Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:15.70,Freezing Main Think,On The Door,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad2\t(\fs22)\move(426,257,444,232,0,8702)}男士禁入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:11.74,Freezing Main,Yumi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}体检完的女生 \N请排队进行下一项检查!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:13.92,Freezing Main,Elis,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这些是胸围测量的卷尺.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:15.71,Freezing Main,Elis,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你们可以互相测量.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.03,Freezing Main,Hiiragi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}拉娜同学, 81 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:19.80,Freezing Main,Hiiragi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好了, 我们换把.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:23.00,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我为什么要用卷尺.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Freezing Main,Hiiragi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:25.66,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}圣门八极拳的基础! {[Seimon Hakkyokuken, for you who wish to retain the literal version]}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.66,0:00:27.21,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}通过感知来测量!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:29.14,Freezing Main,Hiiragi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你干啥呢?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:31.18,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}柊同学, 77 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:33.34,Freezing Main,Hiiragi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}等等, 这就完了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:37.52,Freezing Main,Hiiragi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我还希望能大一点呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:39.20,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}会慢慢成长的,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.71,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因为你还处在成长期嘛.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:43.84,Freezing Main,Ganessa,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}天啊，这样还真是方便呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:47.86,Freezing Main,Ganessa,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你，过来，来量量我吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哇!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:51.23,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那确实值得测量!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:52.65,Freezing Main,Hiiragi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}真，真大!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:55.14,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}让我看看.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:57.78,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你是 83 cm, 加尼莎同学.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Freezing Main,Ganessa,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}噢!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:01.79,Freezing Main,Ganessa,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}或许我有些成长过了.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:07.00,Freezing Main,Hiiragi,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那个坏笑是啥意思?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.97,0:01:07.00,Freezing Overlap,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:09.29,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}莎特莱萨.L.布里兹!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:10.80,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哇, 90 cm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:14.21,Freezing Main,Satella,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这就是我讨厌体检的原因.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:17.78,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}啥，你讨厌?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:21.01,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我是最讨厌这个的了.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:24.80,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}学生会长, 西冯 菲尔查尔德, 82 cm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:29.74,Freezing Main,Rana,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}副会长, 堤希.菲尼尔, 83 cm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:34.00,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}看来我逃不掉了.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:37.70,Freezing Main,Chiffon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}阿蒂亚同学, 你在这边干什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:40.14,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}学生会长 西冯.菲尔查尔德!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:42.34,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:45.66,Freezing Main,Chiffon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你在这看起来很郁闷.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:48.12,Freezing Main,Chiffon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:49.83,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没，没什么啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:55.59,Freezing Main,Chiffon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这样的话, 我来给你量量吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:58.03,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不，不用，这样就好!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:00.48,Freezing Main,Chiffon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}来吧, 别那么害羞!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:04.08,Freezing Main,Chiffon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我来看看... 73 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.62,Freezing Main,Chiffon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}好可爱!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:07.60,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"可爱"? 这是讽刺么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:11.97,Freezing Main,Chiffon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}不, 小胸围也可以是很迷人的哦l.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:13.37,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}小!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:15.36,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}这还不如被叫做‘可爱’呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.18,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}你个坏女人!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:20.06,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我要让你看看我可以用伏特着装来扩大我的胸围!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:24.24,Freezing Main,Chiffon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}没必要了. 还是我给你继续测量吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:28.22,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}那... 不... 不必劳驾了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:31.38,Freezing Main,Chiffon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我相信我可以把这个小胸部变得漂亮的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.33,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}别再说小了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:40.05,Freezing Main,Attia,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}胸部... 不需要... 仅仅... 大... 还有色泽都会影响...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.78,0:02:40.05,Freezing Overlap,Chiffon,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\an8}完了么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:45.71,Freezing Main,Kazuya,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我虔诚的向上帝祈祷让这种平静可以永存吧.
